snippet.title: Rosa's Garden Release Trailer
snippet.description:
A calm gardening game with roses.

Find seeds, place pits and grow your roses. Over 40 breeding combinations to discover new roses in this poetic flower game. All the roses are named after famous women, paying a small tribute to their lives and achievements.

Get it now:
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.CharlotteMadelon.RosasGardenApp
App Store: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/rosas-garden/id1454842114?l=nl&ls=1&mt=8

Developed by Charlotte Madelon
Audio created by Martin Mathiesen Kvale
